咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaece0b71f6cf83d381c8c1d61f21c1df2945774","tid":1123743,"uid":192090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a63818adcf4f37f54f897381d18cd13045588b0","tid":1123743,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"我都想無情感波動，但呢幾日個人真係好down"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"我都係，好想個人無情感，呢個幾星期人唔似人，鬼唔似鬼咁"},{"pid":"3a68473f03267caae7f346c3f190fe2b8cdc9fd7","tid":1123743,"uid":224831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4565c6b8bc060458e9bbe75c0f58979036387bbb","tid":1123743,"uid":200914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc762fd42c28c9bee333daf6f63cb8e3d4ae50d6","tid":1123743,"uid":224831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"768cee2c2a265ef711ddc883e731baee43aa8d12","tid":1123743,"uid":200914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T12:03:29.000Z","msg":"你嘅定義係，我嘅定義唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實覺得有得有失嘅，可能係習慣上咗有感情起伏嘅感覺，唔係而家呢種 太冷靜嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有過其實都知足，但係就想要更多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"ching實際分佐手幾耐啦？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你係一齊之前，已經覺得自己係一個冇情感波動既人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:02:54.000Z","msg":"一個月內啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想自己down咁耐<br />\n其實係由f5開始，好多做咗好多年嘅嘢（有挑戰性）都因為要準備升大而被逼放低曬，本來習慣咗喺壓力下生活，一抽離咗成個人都覺得好奇怪，好唔適應呢種感覺<br />\n加上本身同屋企人關係唔算好，成日一無事做就去翻pt，咁多年嚟對住屋企人同啲閪客，都磨到無曬脾氣<br />\n搞到而家又唔識開心，又唔識嬲，咩都唔無所謂<br />\n但係遇到佢之後，就開始有翻正常感情咁嘅感覺，仲第一次感受到原來在乎，擔心一個人係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T21:22:13.000Z","msg":"聽落感覺你係因為呢一刻冇自己重視既人／事，所以冇野可以牽動到自己既情緒<br />\n升大學、屋企人、客，或者未係自己好重視既人同事，潛意識就放空自己，唔想投放感情去面對<br />\n而ex既話，因為係自己好在乎既人，所以會被佢牽動到自己既情緒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ddf68adda00cbbf19ce7d5f1b0cca490a813c6","tid":1123743,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"無感情好過一直唔開心啊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0264422ab98accea4a46f0ffc78927a2156c66c","tid":1123743,"uid":56475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffa9e8a26cf9005b7df166de9dbec540cddc4a4a","tid":1123743,"uid":200914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"因為拍拖，終於有翻啲人嘅情感<br />\n識得發自內心咁擔心人，笑同喊<br />\n心痛，甚至成為自己仲係人嘅最大證明<br />\n但而家，對所有嘢都可以坦然/無所謂<br />\n好似冇咗做人嘅七情六慾，變翻以前咁，就算有壓力我都冇feel<br />\n好唔鍾意而家嘅自己<br />\n究竟點樣做，先可以感覺似翻個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:15:00.000Z","msg":"散左？"},{"pid":"9ee56cdcabc7d2e3898916768ce64198cf4d1416","tid":1123743,"uid":56475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"我近期都好down 我都散左。"},{"pid":"7c64c1cda0434d69e7d4d07d2830eb048831f1bd","tid":1123743,"uid":145882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afba1176b9d032ed576ca6d62eee1220516987cc","tid":1123743,"uid":200914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"521e43df0d76c78f731b18941220a898fe4598f5","tid":1123743,"uid":145882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"同我拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:49:41.000Z","msg":"乜又係你啊陳生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"邊個淫蕩呀你淫蕩"},{"pid":"664aff067c8b35e264bac248822a884fd2a684e5","tid":1123743,"uid":200914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49ddf68adda00cbbf19ce7d5f1b0cca490a813c6","tid":1123743,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"無感情好過一直唔開心啊..